  m_Text: "Terms of Use of the \u201CTrading profit\u201D App\n\nThese Terms of Use
    define the procedure and conditions for using the \u201CTrading profit\u201D
    mobile application (the \u201CApp\u201D). Before you start using the App, please
    read these Terms carefully.\n\n1. Acceptance of Terms\n\nBy starting to use the
    App, you confirm your agreement with these Terms. If any provisions of these
    Terms are unacceptable to you, please refrain from using the App.\n\n2. App Description\n\n\u201CTrading
    profit\u201D is a mobile solution for organizing financial flows, tracking funds,
    and analyzing expenses. With the App, you can monitor your budget, set financial
    goals, and receive practical recommendations to improve your financial situation.\n\n3.
    Rules of Use\n\t\u2022\tThe App must be used only in compliance with applicable
    laws.\n\t\u2022\tYou are responsible for maintaining the security of access to
    your device and accounts.\n\t\u2022\tIt is prohibited to use the App to distribute
    malware or harmful content.\n\t\u2022\tWhen using the App, it is important to
    provide accurate and up-to-date information.\n\n4. Privacy and Data Processing\n\nThe
    collection and processing of your data is carried out in strict accordance with
    our Privacy Policy. We ensure the protection of your personal information and
    use it solely to improve the App\u2019s functionality.\n\n5. Intellectual Property
    Rights\n\nAll rights to the App and its content, including text, graphics, logos,
    images, and other materials, belong to the developer or to third parties who
    have granted the rights to use such materials.\n\n6. Limitation of Liability\n\nThe
    App is provided \u201Cas is,\u201D and the developer shall not be liable for
    any losses or damages arising from the use of, or inability to use, the App.\n\n7.
    Changes to the Terms\n\nWe reserve the right to amend these Terms at any time.
    All changes will be published in this document, and the date of the latest revision
    will be updated.\n\n8. Termination of Use\n\nYou may stop using the App at any
    time without any additional conditions. If violations of these Rules are identified,
    we reserve the right to restrict or completely terminate your access to the App\u2019s
    functionality.\n\n9. Contact Information\n\nIf you have any questions or suggestions
    regarding the use of the App, please contact us at: feedback@moneymind.com.\n\n\xA9
    2024 \u201CTrading profit\u201D. All rights reserved.\n\n\u2E3B\n\nPrivacy Policy
    of the \u201CTrading profit\u201D App\n\nIn the \u201CTrading profit\u201D app
    (the \u201CApp\u201D), we place the highest priority on protecting your privacy.
    This Policy explains how we collect and process information when you use the
    App, and describes the measures we take to ensure security.\n\n1. Information
    We Collect\n\nWe follow a data-minimization principle and collect only the information
    necessary:\n\t\u2022\tTechnical data: Basic information about your device - type,
    OS version, technical identifiers, and network parameters required for the App
    to function properly.\n\t\u2022\tUsage data: Information about how you interact
    with the App - session duration, visited sections, and actions performed - to
    help us improve user experience.\n\n2. How We Use Information\n\nWe use collected
    data only for the following purposes:\n\t\u2022\tEnsuring the App operates properly,
    including displaying features and improving the interface.\n\t\u2022\tAnalyzing
    App usage to improve functionality and optimize user experience.\n\t\u2022\tSending
    notifications about important updates or changes in the App (optional).\n\n3.
    Data Security\n\nWe do not collect or store sensitive personal data (such as
    credit card numbers, addresses, or passwords). All collected data is protected
    using standard security measures, and access to it is restricted.\n\n4. Sharing
    Data with Third Parties\n\nWe do not share your personal information with third
    parties except in the following cases:\n\t\u2022\tWhen required by law or to
    comply with legal obligations.\n\t\u2022\tWhen we share data with partners or
    service providers to improve the App\u2019s functionality (for example, analytics
    services). In such cases, they are required to protect your information.\n\n5.
    Use of Cookies\n\nWe do not use cookies to collect personal information. However,
    to improve performance and user experience, the App may use standard cookies
    that store information about your device and actions within the App. You can
    configure your browser to reject cookies, but this may affect some features.\n\n6.
    Your Rights\n\nSince the App does not systematically collect personal data, issues
    related to accessing or deleting such data are not applicable. Use of the App
    is voluntary and can be discontinued by you at any time.\n\n7. Changes to This
    Privacy Policy\n\nWe reserve the right to change this Privacy Policy at any time.
    All changes will be published on this page with an updated date. Please review
    updates periodically.\n\n8. Contact Information\n\nIf you have any questions
    or suggestions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: feedback@moneymind.com.\n\n\xA9
    2025 \u201CTrading profit\u201D. All rights reserved."
